  "description": "This individual presents as an animate corpse, with taut taupe skin drawn tight over prominent bone and joints set in a permanent, misaligned rigidity. Gray eyes remain glassy and unfocused, while brown hair persists in a sparse, uneven growth along the scalp. The face bears fissure-scored pitting and old fracture lines that never seal, leaving the jaw slightly offset and the teeth exposed in a fixed rictus. The overall frame is desiccated and angular, marking prolonged unlife in a harsh, abrasive environment.",
